text: The French-language surname Rousset may refer to: * Alain Rousset (born 1951), French politician * Christophe Rousset, French conductor and harpsichordist * Gilles Rousset, French footballer * David Rousset, French writer and prisoner in the German Neuengamme concentration camp * Jean Rousset, Swiss literary critic and theorist, often associated with the Geneva School of literary criticism Category:French-language surnames
title: Rousset (surname)
